            terms_title: "Responsible use of .skv",
            terms_body: "<p>.skv is an experimental tool created by a writer to help other writers work with more privacy and focus.</p><p>By using this system, you understand and agree that:</p><ul><li>.skv is provided ‚Äúas is‚Äù, without any express or implied warranties.</li><li>Failures may occur, including software bugs, data loss, file corruption, browser issues, device or operating system failures, power outages, crashes, misuse, or local environment limitations.</li><li>Although the system has been extensively tested, no software is infallible.</li><li>Responsibility for exporting, backing up, storing, and protecting your texts lies entirely with the user.</li></ul><p>.skv does not guarantee legal authorship, official registration, legal validity, or absolute protection of any text. Hashes, metadata, and technical records may constitute mathematical evidence of prior existence, but they do not replace formal legal registration.</p><p>The author of .skv assumes no liability for losses, direct or indirect damages, loss of profits, service interruptions, misuse of the system, authorship claims, or unmet expectations.</p><p>Current limits: up to 200 notes and 30 folders.</p><p>By accepting these terms, you acknowledge that:</p><ul><li>you are using an independent tool,</li><li>created as a technical and cultural experiment,</li><li>without formal support or service guarantees,</li><li>and that you assume full responsibility for how you use it.</li></ul><p>If you understand and accept these terms, you may begin.</p>",
